# Description

This plugin provides access to full episodes of The Daily Show, as well as extended guest interviews.

# Installation

Simply click the "download as ZIP" link on the GitHub repository page, copy the zip file to your XMBC and find the "install from ZIP" command in the addon settings.

# Credits

This project was originally forked from: https://github.com/VTWoods/xbmc-dailyshow
The second form came from: https://github.com/adamsb6/xbmc-dailyshow

[BeautifulSoup](http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/) is used to scrape web content.

